## Part 2: Streamlit Web App — `hiv_protease-main/`

A **Streamlit web dashboard** to present results visually.

### Running the App
```bash
cd hiv_protease-main
pip install -r requirements.txt  # if requirements exist, otherwise install manually
streamlit run app.py
```
> **Note**: The app has a `venv/` folder with ~22,000 files, meaning a Python virtual environment is already set up. You would activate it first, or install dependencies manually (`streamlit`, `rdkit`, `py3Dmol`, `stmol`).

